    - stash_sha: "acae4bb5029e61ff301c92eed0e9679a1954a792"
      subject: "On main: auto-reconcile-20260416-055517-stephans-mac-mini"
      decision: superseded
      reason: "Reviewed 2026-05-09. Only changes .claude/research.md with an older long-form research document. Current repo state uses the compact research cache plus promoted findings; this is not release behavior or live docs."
    - stash_sha: "fef590105b91cc92b93a0635b9faeead1cf64eec"
      subject: "On main: auto-reconcile-20260415-215519-stephans-mac-mini"
      decision: superseded
      reason: "Reviewed 2026-05-09. Removes the current 1.1.6 changelog entry. HEAD already documents the live release notes for 1.1.6, so this stash is older release-note residue."
    - stash_sha: "8e7d4432007773028fe939fa2e011b593b0d3080"
      subject: "On main: auto-reconcile-20260415-055522-stephans-mac-mini"
