      reason: "Reviewed 2026-05-09. Older pre-1.1.5/pre-1.1.6 state: .saneprocess re-enables the App Store lane, CHANGELOG loses the 1.1.5/1.1.6 entries, README/site copy regresses, and key app/menu files drop the current Dock/menu Settings/License/About flow now present in HEAD."
    - stash_sha: "85401e38e0b484f64e6fbc84855446c2ebec692a"
